  <summary date="2024-02-23T16:16:33Z" status="Introduced in House">End Tax Breaks for Dark Money Act 

This bill extends the capital gains tax on transfers of appreciated property to certain tax-exempt social organizations (e.g., civics leagues, agricultural organizations, or business leagues). Currently, the tax is imposed only on transfers to political organizations.</summary>
